thread.title_full: Liberty's Amanda Rachwal is lehighvalleylive Girls Volleyball Player of the Week

title: Liberty's Amanda Rachwal is lehighvalleylive Girls Volleyball Player of the Week
text:
It was a good week for several Hurricanes, especially the junior middle hitter, as second-ranked Liberty went 3-0, including a five-set victory over Bethlehem Catholic. 
Rachwal tallied 46 kills and eight blocks as Liberty topped Easton, Dieruff and Becahi. 
She recorded 21 kills and three blocks as the Hurricanes outlasted the Golden Hawks in what was probably the match of the season so far. 
Honorable mention : Jr. MH Alyson Bohman , Emmaus; Sr. S Maddie Capuano , Liberty; So. OH Leanna Deegan , Easton; Sr. S Kristin Krause , Parkland; Sr. MH Nioami Miranda , Hackettstown; So. MH Grace Mittl , Liberty; Sr. MH Amy Radzelovage , Freedom; Jr. Chandra Ramlogan , Voorhees; Jr. MH/OH Dana Roberts , Central Catholic; So. OH Julia Roman , Freedom; Sr. OP Siena Salvaggio , Parkland.
